Testcase:3 (PVR Cinemas)
================

01)Launch the URL https://www.pvrcinemas.com/
02)Choose your location as Chennai.
03)Click on "Cinema" under Quick Book.
04)Select the cinema: PVR AEROHUB Chennai.
05)Select the date: Tomorrow's date.
06)Select the movie: The first movie on the list.
07)Select the timing: The first available timing.
08)Click on "Book".
09)Click on "Accept" for Terms and Conditions.
10)Click on "First Available Seat".
11)Print the Booking Summary.
12)Print the Grand Total Value.